# 📚 Library Management System

## 📌 Description

A web-based Library Management System built using Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, Spring Data JPA, and Oracle Database. The application allows efficient management of books, students, and book issue/return operations.

## 🚀 Features

* Manage Books (Add, Update, Delete, View)
* Manage Students (Add, Update, Delete, View)
* Issue Books to Students
* Return Issued Books
* Automatic Book Quantity Management
* Track Issue and Return Dates
* Simple and Responsive UI

## 🛠 Tech Stack

* Java 17
* Spring Boot
* Spring Data JPA
* Thymeleaf
* Bootstrap 5
* Oracle Database
* Maven

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Abeer200529/LibraryManagementSystem.git
cd LibraryManagementSystem
mvn spring-boot:run
```

Open:
http://localhost:8080


##ScreenShort
* Dashboard
* Student
* IssueRecord
